nodes.text: The Razzi warehouse raid was robbery of the Razzi Syndicate that had occurred by 10 BBY. In the aftermath of the raid, stolen cargo was recieved by the rivial criminal orginization Crimson Dawn. Qi'ra, lieutenant to Crimson Dawn leader Dryden Vos, recorded details of the stolen cargo in the logbook known as the Smuggler's Guide, which had also been acquired in the raid.
